thread.title: Gisa 21

author: Gisa 21
title: Gisa 21
text: I am surprised about this product. You can easily shape and design your own brows in a few minutes. The result is very natural. However, a negative point is, that the product doesn't cover gaps very well, so that you have to fill them with a brow pencil after application of Wonder 2. Despite this point I am very satisfied with quality and pigmentation. I clearly recommend the purchase of Wonder 2 !
